{"content": "I need to multiply 280 \u00d7 349 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 280\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 280\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 8\u00d711\u00b9 + 0\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 8\u00d711 + 0\n- = 242 + 88 + 0\n- = 330\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 349\u2081\u2081 to base 10**\n- 349\u2081\u2081 = 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 9\u00d711\u2070\n- = 3\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 9\n- = 363 + 44 + 9\n- = 416\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 330 \u00d7 416 = 137,280\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 137,280\u2081\u2080 to base 11**\n- 137,280 \u00f7 11 = 12,480 R 0\n- 12,480 \u00f7 11 = 1,134 R 6\n- 1,134 \u00f7 11 = 103 R 1\n- 103 \u00f7 11 = 9 R 4\n- 9 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 9\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 94160\u2081\u2081\n\n94160", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 373}